    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a great value with this reliable daily driver! While it shows some honest wear from its years on the road, it remains a solid and dependable choice for anyone looking for practical transportation. It's a well-loved vehicle with plenty of life left, perfect for someone who prioritizes function and character over a showroom finish!",
