      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, some minor dings, and the clear coat is starting to show wear on the roof and hood. Inside, the cabin is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely require some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to keep it in optimal shape. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at a budget-friendly price point.",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition, looking and performing exactly as it did the day it was first sold. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep shine and no scratches or chips, and the interior remains in showroom state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine is incredibly responsive, and every component functions as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously cared-for vehicle that requires no immediate attention and offers a premium driving experience.",
      "price": 47500.0,
